      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for value. The exterior has some minor scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need some routine maintenance like new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that has been used regularly but still has plenty of life left.",
