    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously maintained, making it a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands the very best. Don't miss your chance to own this flawless masterpiece!",
