    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine has a noticeable knock and struggles to stay running, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. Cosmetically, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the paint is peeling in multiple areas. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, and several electronic features, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts.",
